name: Brown Backpack DAO
description:
DAO supporting the Brown Backpack Guy (@bejzik8) attending crypto conferences for the next 3 years.

- donation will be used to cover tickets and flights for Brown Backpack Guy over the next 2 Devcons and other global ETH events: ie. ETHCC and Devconnect

- community member can vote and approve which crypto developer events and parties Brown Backpack Guy should attend

- the rest of the donation will be used to run social media, and protecc web3 communities from baseless social media harassment, cancel culture and toxic anon doxes
